[DOCUMENT]
TITLE: Operational Needs
UID: DOC-OPN
VERSION: 0.1-draft
CLASSIFICATION: Public

[FREETEXT]
This document captures the **operational needs** that the Molten Light
telescope must satisfy, stated in natural language, without the word
"shall". Operational needs are the raw input from which Phase A will derive
Stakeholder Requirements (STNR-*) and subsequently System Requirements
(SYSR-*). This document is therefore intentionally *pre-requirement*.

Each entry below is a skeleton stub with UID, title, and a TODO placeholder
for the actual need statement. The full set of needs will be populated in a
subsequent working session, one stakeholder category at a time, using the
stakeholder analysis as the index.
[/FREETEXT]

