[FREETEXT]
# TODO — additional needs to add in the next session

- Public engineering record as an explicit deliverable (mission objective 4,
  stakeholder 5 and 6).
- Seeing-limited on-sky performance (mission success criterion 2).
- Long operational lifetime with scheduled maintenance (mission lifetime
  section, stakeholder 12).
- Compliance with site-specific regulatory regime (stakeholder 8 and 9).
- Credit and licence clarity for collaborators (stakeholder 11).
- Data products usable by citizen-science and educational workflows
  (stakeholders 3 and 4).
- Safe-by-default failure behaviour across all subsystems (ConOps
  off-nominal operations).

Target count: 10 to 15 numbered needs. Add in one working session, not
drip-fed over many.
[/FREETEXT]
